title: Strömvallen
text: Strömvallen is a <a href="association%20football">football</a> <a href="stadium">stadium</a> in <a href="G%C3%A4vle">Gävle</a>, <a href="Sweden">Sweden</a>. It was the home ground of <a href="Gefle%20IF">Gefle IF</a> until 2015. The stadium holds 6,703 people and was initially opened in 1903, with a dedicated spectator area built in 1923.
